# AI Safety Concepts

Prompt-based AI safety and character consistency techniques developed independently.

## Concepts

### DNA-Lock
Text-based character anchoring technique for AI image generation.
Achieves consistent character identity without LoRA or model training.

### Pincet Defense  
Selective security layer for LLM pipelines.
Intervenes only when threat patterns are detected, preserving normal performance.

### Muse vs Muse
Adversarial same-capability LLM structure for attack pattern data collection.
Uses LLM's self-proving tendency as a data extraction mechanism.

